The paper discusses the combination of deep learning and reinforcement learning, which is a common topic in the machine learning community and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus of the paper is on continuous control tasks, which are related to robotics and control systems, suggesting that it could also fall under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions tasks with high state and action dimensionality, which could involve computer vision techniques and therefore fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper evaluates a range of reinforcement learning algorithms, which could also place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
